data.description: Welcome to this fantastic rambler perched in the highly sought-after neighborhood, Brasswood, in south Edmond. This home offers single-level living at its finest with 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 well-appointed bathrooms, and two separate living spaces. The open floor plan and 12ft ceilings in the main living area offer the ideal entertaining space for family and friends while enjoying the convenience of a newly remolded kitchen, pantry, and designated dining area. With fresh finishes and an inviting ambiance, this home combines contemporary style with comfort. Recent updates include a new roof and gutters (June 2023), New Paint, Carpet, Toilets, and Recently replaced flooring throughout and water heaters.
